      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Brevan Howard 削减 100 多名员工以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/brevan-howard-cuts-more-than-100-staff-in-cost-cutting-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Brevan Howard 资产管理公司将裁员 10%——或大约 100 名员工——随着世界上最著名的对冲基金巨头之一精简其快速增长的业务，以降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/brevan-howard-cuts-more-than-100-staff-in-cost-cutting-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:39:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Fortress 支持的 Brightline 要求投资者押注佛罗里达铁路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/fortress-backed-brightline-asks-investors-to-bet-on-florida-rail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Brightline 是一个多世纪以来第一家新的美国私人客运铁路，它相信它可以吸引更多的佛罗里达人不再乘坐汽车——但首先，它正在为大约 40 亿美元的债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/fortress-backed-brightline-asks-investors-to-bet-on-florida-rail</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
